OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775106076
OL,3,CCousin of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Csays families have not received justice
OL,6,FThe cousin of a Bristol man, who was
OL,7,Fone of seven aid workers killed in an
OL,8,FIsraeli air strike two years ago, says
OL,9,Ftheir families have still not received
OL,10,Fjustice.
OL,12,FJames Kirby, an armed forces veteran,
OL,13,Fwas delivering food to Palestinians in
OL,14,FGaza with the World Central Kitchen
OL,15,Fcharity when he was killed on 1 April
OL,16,F2024. Two other Britons, John Chapman,
OL,17,Ffrom Dorset, and James "Jim" Henderson
OL,18,Ffrom Cornwall, also lost their lives.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
