FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775106076
OL,3,CCousin of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Csays families have not received justice
OL,6,FJames Kirby's cousin, Louise, says her
OL,7,Ffamily's contact with the UK
OL,8,FGovernment has been "limited" and she
OL,9,Fisn't sure whether an investigation
OL,10,Finto his death is underway.
OL,12,FIn a statement released on the second
OL,13,Fanniversary of his death, she said:
OL,14,F"James was deeply loved by our family,
OL,15,Fremembered not only for his courage,
OL,16,Fcompassion, and dedication to helping
OL,17,Fothers, but also for his warm
OL,18,Fpersonality and brilliant sense of
OL,19,Fhumour that could brighten any room.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775106076
OL,3,CCousin of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Csays families have not received justice
OL,6,F"It is especially difficult to see
OL,7,Fthat men who were so loyal and
OL,8,Fcommitted to their country have not
OL,9,Fyet received the justice they deserve.
OL,11,F"Two years on, communication from the
OL,12,Fgovernment has been limited, and the
OL,13,Ffamily remains unsure whether a full
OL,14,Fand formal investigation is underway.
OL,16,F"We respectfully ask the Foreign
OL,17,FSecretary to make direct contact with
OL,18,Fthe families and provide a clear plan
OL,19,Ffor truth, justice, and
OL,20,Faccountability."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775106076
OL,3,CCousin of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Csays families have not received justice
OL,6,FIn response, the Minister for the
OL,7,FMiddle East, Hamish Falconer, said:
OL,8,F"The UK government has pressed Israel
OL,9,Fat the highest level for answers.
OL,10,FIsrael has a responsibility to provide
OL,11,Fthese.
OL,13,F"I've heard firsthand the pain their
OL,14,Ffamilies have endured. So today, I
OL,15,Frepeat the UK's call for transparency
OL,16,Fand accountability for this appalling
OL,17,Fattack - we will continue to push for
OL,18,Fjustice.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775106076
OL,3,CCousin of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Csays families have not received justice
OL,6,F"No aid worker should be killed doing
OL,7,Ftheir job providing lifesaving care to
OL,8,Fcivilians living in the most dire
OL,9,Fstraits.
OL,11,F"I urge Israel to swiftly conclude and
OL,12,Fpublish their findings into this
OL,13,Fattack. The families of those killed
OL,14,Fmust know why this happened. Lessons
OL,15,Fmust be learned. A tragedy like this
OL,16,Fmust never happen again."
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
